%h2 Experiment Feedback
%p#feedback
  The Microbial Imaging Facility wishes to monitor the performance of this instrument. Additionally MIF staff are also available for experimental trouble shooting if an imaging experiment is unsuccessful. If the instrument was faulty or your experiment did not work please fill out the quick survey below. Otherwise go to the submit button to logout.

.container
  = render_field "Experiment Name", '  ' + @experiment.expt_name
  = render_field "Created At", @experiment.created_at.localtime.strftime('  %d-%m-%Y %H:%M')
%p
= simple_form_for [@experiment_feedback] do |f|
  = f.input :experiment_failed, label:"Experiment failed?"
  = f.input :instrument_failed, label:"Instrument failed?"
  = f.input :instrument_failed_reason
  = f.input :other_comments

  .form-actions
    = f.submit "Submit", :class => "btn btn-primary", :id => "experiment_feedback_submit"